issue.title: Privacy Policy
issue.body: We need one to submit to the App Store

issue.title: Wifi not connected
issue.body: Currently, APIs don't work if the phone cannot connect to the API endpoints (say, if wifi/data were turned off), but there isn't any indication to the user that this might be the case. Add this functionality.

issue.title: Improve ML recognition
issue.body: Currently, ML recognition is quite primitive. Improve this in some way.

issue.title: Android compatibility
issue.body: Currently, the project does not compile to Android. Fix this.

issue.title: Card order
issue.body:
Cards are currently stored in order of creation with the oldest cards on top. Two things should change:

1. Flip the default order such that the newest cards are at the top.

2. Allow users to change card order

issue.title: QR code sending pictures
issue.body: Currently, QR code scanning doesn't send the picture associated with the flashcard. Add this functionality.

issue.title: UAuth
issue.body: Auth does not currently exist. It should be set up to hold all currently locally-stored userdata.

issue.title: Card conversion
issue.body:
As it stands, cards created in a particular language remain in that language, and any conversion must be done manually. Two features should be added to allow bulk and individual card conversion:

1. Add a button to the "Edit Card" view which allows users to set the new target language for a particular card. The "foreign" value should be automatically translated using the inputted "native" value.

2. Add a button to the "Settings" view which converts all cards into the current target language.

commits.message: Use the card’s lang when speaking it
Remove unsupported language with no comment on its legitimacy
Add app icon & launch screen for iOS
Fancy animation when a card is created
Show spinner wjhen running API queries
TTS in the language of the text (kinda)
